Privacy Policy for AssetXpense

Effective date: 3 May 2026

AssetXpense does not collect, store, or share any personal data on external servers.

All user data is stored securely using Apple's iCloud services and remains under the user's control. The developer of AssetXpense does not have access to this data.

Data Usage:
- All financial or personal data entered into the app is stored in the user’s private iCloud account.
- No data is transmitted to third-party servers.
- No analytics, tracking, or advertising tools are used.

iCloud:
AssetXpense uses Apple iCloud to sync and store user data across devices. This data is managed by Apple in accordance with their Privacy Policy.

Third-Party Services:
The app does not use any third-party services that collect user data.

